ЁЭРАЁЭРЪЁЭРеЁЭРЪЁЭРй ЁЭРТЁЭРнЁЭРоЁЭРЭЁЭРвЁЭРи ЁЭРПЁЭРлЁЭРЮЁЭРмЁЭРЮЁЭРзЁЭРнЁЭРм:- New Nepali Tele Serial ЁЭРМЁЭРАЁЭРШЁЭРАЁЭРКЁЭРО ЁЭРВЁЭРЗЁЭРИЁЭРНЁЭРО ЁЭРДЁЭРПЁЭРИЁЭРТЁЭРОЁЭРГЁЭРД-ЁЭЯПЁЭЯС Only on Aalap Studio Official Youtube Channel  

"ЁЭРМЁЭРАЁЭРШЁЭРАЁЭРКЁЭРО ЁЭРВЁЭРЗЁЭРИЁЭРНЁЭРО" Teleserial is a female-dominated telefilm that seeks to portray the reality of what is happening in society. How many children are orphaned in Nepal due to the distortion and inconsistency in love relationships.

"MAYAKO CHINO " is a telefilm that seeks to show the impact of interracial love affair on society between rich and poor.

Getting education is a child's right, but many children in Nepal have not been able to go to school because they do not have good parents.

   The caterpillar of the tele-serial, Kamala, who herself has struggled a lot to read and will go on a separate campaign tomorrow to teach such children who do not have good parents.

en.description:
ЁЭРАЁЭРЪЁЭРеЁЭРЪЁЭРй ЁЭРТЁЭРнЁЭРоЁЭРЭЁЭРвЁЭРи ЁЭРПЁЭРлЁЭРЮЁЭРмЁЭРЮЁЭРзЁЭРнЁЭРм:- New Nepali Tele Serial ЁЭРМЁЭРАЁЭРШЁЭРАЁЭРКЁЭРО ЁЭРВЁЭРЗЁЭРИЁЭРНЁЭРО ЁЭРДЁЭРПЁЭРИЁЭРТЁЭРОЁЭРГЁЭРД-ЁЭЯПЁЭЯС Only on Aalap Studio Official Youtube Channel  

"ЁЭРМЁЭРАЁЭРШЁЭРАЁЭРКЁЭРО ЁЭРВЁЭРЗЁЭРИЁЭРНЁЭРО" Teleserial is a female-dominated telefilm that seeks to portray the reality of what is happening in society. How many children are orphaned in Nepal due to the distortion and inconsistency in love relationships.

"MAYAKO CHINO " is a telefilm that seeks to show the impact of interracial love affair on society between rich and poor.

Getting education is a child's right, but many children in Nepal have not been able to go to school because they do not have good parents.

   The caterpillar of the tele-serial, Kamala, who herself has struggled a lot to read and will go on a separate campaign tomorrow to teach such children who do not have good parents.
